      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.210-1</ph> Market Research.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3140e8" class="- topic/p ">As prescribed
in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1114778.dita#i1114778"
                     base="i1114778"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">10.003</xref>
            </ph>, insert the
following clause:</p>
         <p rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020"
            outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps"
            class="- topic/p "><?FM MARKER [Why] FAR Case 2018-007?>Market
Research (Jun 2020)<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 52.210-1 by—
a. Revising the date of the clause;?></p>
         <ol id="d3102e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3140e18" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Definition</i>.
As used in this clause—</p>
               <p id="d3140e24" class="- topic/p ">
                  <i outputclass="Term"
                     xtrc="d3133e40"
                     xtrf="_52.210-1"
                     class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Commercial item</i> and
“nondevelopmental item” have the meaning contained in Federal Acquisition <ph rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-007?>Regulation (FAR)<?FM MARKER [Why] b. In paragraph (a), removing from the definition of “Commercial item” and “nondevelopmental item” the word “Regulation” and adding “Regulation (FAR)” in its place; and?></ph> 
                  <xref href="FAR-i1125359.dita#i1125359"
                        base="i1125359"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3140e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>Before awarding
subcontracts over the simplified acquisition <ph rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-007?>threshold, as defined in FAR <xref href="FAR-i1125359.dita#i1125359"
                           base="i1125359"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref> on the date of subcontract
award,<?FM MARKER [Why] c. Removing from the introductory text of paragraph (b) “threshold” and adding “threshold, as defined in FAR 2.101 on the date of subcontract award,” in its place.?></ph> for items other than commercial items, the Contractor
shall conduct market research to—</p>
               <ol id="d3102e56" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3140e38" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>Determine if
commercial items or, to the extent commercial items suitable to
meet the agency’s needs are not available, nondevelopmental items
are available that–</p>
                     <ol id="d3102e66" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d3140e44" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>Meet the agency’s requirements;</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d3140e49" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>Could be
modified to meet the agency’s requirements; or</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d3140e54" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>Could
meet the agency’s requirements if those requirements were modified
to a reasonable extent; and</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3140e59" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>Determine
the extent to which commercial items or nondevelopmental items could
be incorporated at the component level.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause" class="- topic/p ">(End of clause)</p>
